,"to":523.04},{"content":"不願意就算了…","from":531.18,"location":2,"to":532.2},{"content":"如果是你的話 會去哪裡散心？","from":534.53,"location":2,"to":537.15},{"content":"我？","from":537.66,"location":2,"to":538.3},{"content":"我的話 應該是爵士樂酒吧…","from":538.93,"location":2,"to":541.18},{"content":"酒吧？喝酒…","from":541.61,"location":2,"to":543.74},{"content":"難道你不能喝酒嗎？","from":544.12,"location":2,"to":546.0},{"content":"在我那個村子裡 要滿20歲才能喝酒","from":546.72,"location":2,"to":549.9},{"content":"啊？","from":550.23,"location":2,"to":550.75},{"content":"我才17歲","from":551.01,"location":2,"to":553.02},{"content":"啊？17？","from":553.62,"location":2,"to":555.21},{"content":"（空軍中尉 伊莉娜·盧米尼斯克）","from":555.45,"location":2,"to":555.9},{"content":"身份證上不是寫著21嗎？\n（空軍中尉 伊莉娜·盧米尼斯克）","from":555.9,"location":2,"to":557.77},{"content":"（空軍中尉 伊莉娜·盧米尼斯克）","from":557.77,"location":2,"to":558.66},{"content":"他們說改為成人比較方便","from":558.87,"location":2,"to":561.61},{"content":"我說你怎麼看起來那麼年輕呢","from":563.38,"location":2,"to":565.52},{"content":"嗯 遵守規矩是軍人應該做的","from":566.17,"location":2,"to":569.92},{"content":"不過 就去那裡好了","from":570.52,"location":2,"to":572.66},{"content":"啊？","from":573.26,"location":2,"to":573.78},{"content":"我說就去爵士樂酒吧","from":574.17,"location":2,"to":576.11},{"content":"既然不能喝酒 那就是你喜歡爵士樂？","from":576.78,"location":2,"to":580.08},{"content":"不是啦！","from":580.35,"location":2,"to":581.31},{"content":"那個…","from":581.72,"location":2,"to":583.29},{"content":"因為你沒去過對吧","from":585.05,"location":2,"to":586.23},{"content":"行吧 那裡也有其他飲料 享受音樂就行了","from":587.03,"location":2,"to":591.46},{"content":"但你為什麼…","from":592.28,"location":2,"to":593.52},{"content":"帶我去就是了！","from":593.55,"location":2,"to":595.78},{"content":"（月亮與萊卡與吸血公主）","from":600.99,"location":2,"to":606.0},{"content":"（11月25日 晚上7：05）","from":606.0,"location":2,"to":609.0},{"content":"還是第一次看到你穿便服","from":613.45,"location":2,"to":615.63},{"content":"彆扭","from":615.98,"location":2,"to":616.86},{"content":"我也是","from":618.05,"location":2,"to":618.61},{"content":"我也是